OL,3,CInfected blood victim brands #15,000
OL,4,CTreloar's college payment 'insulting'
OL,6,FAn infected blood scandal victim has
OL,7,Fbranded the #15,000 payment promised
OL,8,Fto pupils subjected to high-risk
OL,9,Fmedical research at a school in
OL,10,FHampshire "insulting".
OL,12,FRichard Warwick was infected with HIV
OL,13,Fand hepatitis B after receiving blood
OL,14,Fproducts at Treloar's school as part
OL,15,Fof medical treatment for haemophilia,
OL,16,Fwhich he was diagnosed with at three
OL,17,Fyears old.
