OL,4,CTreloar's college payment 'insulting'
OL,6,FHe told BBC Radio 4's Today programme
OL,7,Fhe was "obviously very pleased" that
OL,8,F"we're actually getting closer and
OL,9,Fcloser to the end", adding: "Delighted
OL,10,Fto see that in yesterday's report that
OL,11,Fongoing payments would continue for
OL,12,Flife ` that is a big part of our
OL,13,Fconcerns for the whole community ` and
OL,14,Fthat the Government's going to provide
OL,15,Flegal aid for people to get them
OL,16,Fthrough the various hoops and hurdles
OL,17,Fin order for them to make a successful
OL,18,Fclaim, so that's very welcome."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/5
