OL,4,CTreloar's college payment 'insulting'
OL,6,FBut Mr Warwick said the announced
OL,7,Fpayments of #15,000 for former pupils
OL,8,Fof the college like him were
OL,9,F"derisory" and the Government "seemed
OL,10,Fto have plucked (the amount) out of
OL,11,Fthe air".
OL,13,F"Above that, it's insulting not only
OL,14,Fto the children that managed to live
OL,15,Fthrough what was done to them at the
OL,16,Fschool, but also to the parents of the
OL,17,Fchildren that died ` you know, there's
OL,18,Fyoung teenagers ` and the wider
OL,19,Ffamilies.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/5
