OL,6,F"How they've come up with this figure
OL,7,Fis beyond comprehension to be honest."
OL,9,FThe total estimate of the cost of
OL,10,Finfected blood scandal compensation
OL,11,Fwill be set out in the Budget red
OL,12,Fbook, a Cabinet Office minister has
OL,13,Fsaid.
OL,15,FPaymaster general Nick Thomas-Symonds
OL,16,Fdid not put a figure on the total cost
OL,17,Fwhen asked by Times Radio, but said
OL,18,Fmore than #1 billion had already been
OL,19,Fpaid out.
