OL,6,F"The total estimate will be set out in
OL,7,Fthe Budget red book because there is
OL,8,Fstill work to do on that," he said.
OL,10,FMore people may come forward to apply
OL,11,Ffor compensation as a result of
OL,12,Fincreased publicity due to
OL,13,Fannouncements like the latest one, he
OL,14,Fsaid, which makes costs a moving
OL,15,Fpicture.
OL,17,FThe Government will do "what it takes
OL,18,Fto deliver justice" for infected blood
OL,19,Fvictims, he added.
